{"tid":1433659,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[8月9日] 萬人接機和你飛 建議注意事項","createTime":"2019-08-08T14:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T07:04:20.000Z","uid":242083,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f29b82151eda17c8b049d8d5285ff55200cd1e","tid":1433659,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:13:14.000Z","msg":"聽日係機場和你飛啦<br />\n為左更好迎接旅客，我有少少建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>1. 做個有禮貌嘅香港人，一起和你飛</ins></span><br />\n無論旅客係支持定唔支持反修例運動，<strong>請大家有禮貌地做出回應</strong>，展現香港人嘅文明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果身邊有人發生衝突，高EQ人士可以嘗試制止，其他人士請<strong>拎定手機拍片</strong>，避免好似上次咁俾人屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以及可以同食花生人士解釋發生梗嘅事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>2. 清晰表明：我哋想重建美好香港嘅意願</ins></span><br />\n鑒於外國人其實對香港現時狀況一知半解，示威片段可能令人覺得不安、社會好亂。如果有旅客上前詢問及質疑，請清晰而有禮貌地作出解說。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>3. 切勿衝入機場禁區</ins></span><br />\n我諗呢點唔洗多講啦，大家都強調過好多次。<br />\n不過注意返：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請勿上T1 7樓 離境大堂</span></span>（最新新聞已作禁區處理）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>4. 尊重返AA嘅安排</ins></span><br />\n唔好為難機場職員，增加自己敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以睇返機場管理局附例<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap483A!zh-Hant-HK?fbclid=IwAR1Ksm2CtJf4Zn8f3w4vdxNX3xI2B8h-awjWcHOHgFnbix08WbjqSxKl_IA&amp;m=1&amp;pm=0&amp;pmc=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap483A%21zh-Hant-HK%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Ksm2CtJf4Zn8f3w4vdxNX3xI2B8h-awjWcHOHgFnbix08WbjqSxKl_IA%26m%3D1%26pm%3D0%26pmc%3D1&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9TmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=af3d92a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap483A!zh-Hant-HK?fbclid=IwAR1Ksm2CtJf4Zn8f3w4vdxNX3xI2B8h-awjWcHOHgFnbix08WbjqSxKl_IA&amp;m=1&amp;pm=0&amp;pmc=1</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>5. 帶埋ipad、電腦、擴音器、甚至電視去機場做文宣</ins></span><br />\n用呢啲器材可以展示標語、播片，等遊客更加了解發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如何帶電視請參考：<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403190</a></span><br />\n<br />\n播嘅片最好有唔同語言，優先次序為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文、廣東話</strong></span><br />\n有埋字幕更加好（繁體字幕可以for台灣人）<br />\n<br />\n呢度嘗試整理左video list，大家可以down/mark定先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><em>關於香港警察濫權</em></span><br />\n紐約時報警方濫權報告：Did Hong Kong Police Use Violence Against Protesters? What the Videos Show<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/video/world/asia/100000006602584/hong-kong-police-protest-video-investigation.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Fvideo%2Fworld%2Fasia%2F100000006602584%2Fhong-kong-police-protest-video-investigation.html&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9TmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=fc118704\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/video/world/asia/100000006602584/hong-kong-police-protest-video-investigation.html</a></span><br />\n<br />\n民間記者會：警暴濫權 Hong Kong Police brutality and abuse of power<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://streamable.com/zqhkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fzqhkg&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9TmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=24a736c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/zqhkg</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><em>關於警黑合作</em></span><br />\n鏗鏘集：721元朗黑夜（有英文字幕）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16CiwPChpr0&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D16CiwPChpr0%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9TmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=6e1389a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16CiwPChpr0&amp;feature=youtu.be</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><em>關於來龍去脈</em></span><br />\n攬炒巴團隊中英聯合聲明：Why you should care about Hong Kong: A short introduction to the Sino-British Joint Declaration<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MOpoMURo8pM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMOpoMURo8pM&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9TmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=1d8ce66d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MOpoMURo8pM</a></span><br />\n<br />\n文宣動畫5大訴求：Say No to China Extradition! (English version)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RXAHywPLaD8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRXAHywPLaD8&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9TmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=58ec9248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RXAHywPLaD8</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">注意返：呢度嘅5大訴求係最初版本&mdash;&mdash;係林鄭下台，而非雙普選</span><br />\n<br />\n鏗鏘集：時代革命？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hkfkXgrcc2Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhkfkXgrcc2Y&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9TmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=324d8c65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hkfkXgrcc2Y</a></span><br />\n<br />\nBBC News：楊岳橋：雙普選是北京對香港的承諾<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S2tnk1XH-s4&amp;t=373s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS2tnk1XH-s4%26t%3D373s&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9TmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=031e5b59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S2tnk1XH-s4&amp;t=373s</a></span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎下面補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁聽日見啦各位，祝大家有個愉快嘅旅程<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a012dca1e4906189afda3db878fc882f25de30c4","tid":1433659,"uid":81424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:13:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">89 和你飛 燒衣紙<br />\n810 大埔<br />\n811 深水埗 東區</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[行動post 冇人理]未來數日反送中活動簡報<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1433511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1433511</a>"},{"pid":"977a424c91ee2912d3edcd8a9677ab5e65a44d99","tid":1433659,"uid":184096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:13:59.000Z","msg":"我呼籲所有和理非立即放低電話離開連登<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1433457\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1433457</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9c44ce6a02a5ecd76362a1278e37a5982076896f","tid":1433659,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:15:28.000Z","msg":"自推十連先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1731ea9929d3514ec432f011497df4ba3bcd5a","tid":1433659,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"443dc1a67df5c333bb82f522938ee86b4f1a7681","tid":1433659,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4183f073dd5fffee884949a077284a1c3232438b","tid":1433659,"uid":269301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:16:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"896a89fccdba8472989eb4e245d38bfc404e3e04","tid":1